<div class="mw-translate-fuzzy">
==Utilización==

# Presiona el botón {{KEY|[[Image:Draft ToggleConstructionMode.png|16px]] [[Draft ToggleConstructionMode/es|Alternar modo de construcción]]}} 
# Dibuja algunos objetos
# Presiona el botón {{KEY|[[Image:Draft ToggleConstructionMode.png|16px]] [[Draft ToggleConstructionMode/es|Alternar modo de construcción]]}} de nuevo para volver al modo habitual
</div>

==Notes==

* If Draft construction mode is switched on the active [[Draft_Layer|layer]] is ignored.

==Preferences==

* To change the label of the construction group: {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences → Draft → General → Construction group label}}.
* To change the color that is used: {{MenuCommand|Edit → Preferences → Draft → General → Construction geometry color}}.


